This repository contains the code for a 4-way junction traffic light system. The system is MQTT enabled, allowing updates to be seen and controlled through an app using the MQTT protocol.

Features
4-Way Junction Control: Manages traffic lights for a 4-way intersection.
MQTT Enabled: Real-time updates and control via an MQTT-based app.
Configurable Timings: Easily adjust the duration of red, yellow.

Wokwi Link : https://wokwi.com/projects/405007811293110273

Components:
Esp 32 x 1
Led[Red] x 4
Led[Green] x 4
Led[Blue] x 4
Led[Yellow] x 4
wires x (as needed)
